    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Flame Strike</strong> (Level 5 Evocation)</p><p>A vertical column of divine fire roars down from the heavens in a location you specify. Each creature in a 10-foot-radius, 40-foot-high cylinder centered on a point within range must make a dexterity saving throw. A creature takes 4d6 fire damage and 4d6 radiant damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p><em>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 6th level or higher, the fire damage or the radiant damage (your choice) increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 5th.</em></p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (Pinch of sulfur.)</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> 60 feet | <strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p><p><em>Classes: Cleric</em></p>",
